                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.41/105a.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Special
                        Agent <persName type="to">Carothers</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-02-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 22, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Urge upon Villa the necessity of delivering the body of Benton to relatives or
                    friends requesting same. The failure to deliver body is being made the basis of
                    speculation and bitter criticism.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
